#

Quick Beet Borscht

30 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariandairy-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

main

Tags:

soupquickhealthy

Description

A vibrant, hearty soup packed with flavors and nutrients, made easy with canned beets.

Ingredients

  • canned beets: 2 cans
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potato: 1 large, diced
  • carrot: 1 medium, grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
